, designated by 
<bibRefCitation id="767F43F4A663A74E78F55073412B6AA2" DOI="https://doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.70.9758" author="Aubriot, X" journalOrPublisher="PhytoKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="97 - 110" refId="B9" refString="Aubriot, X, Loup, C, Knapp, S, 2016b. Confirming the identity of two enigmatic &quot;spiny solanums&quot; (Solanum subgenus Leptostemonum, Solanaceae) collected by Jean-Baptiste Leschenault in Java. PhytoKeys 70: 97 - 110, DOI: https://doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.70.9758" title="Confirming the identity of two enigmatic &quot; spiny solanums &quot; (Solanum subgenus Leptostemonum, Solanaceae) collected by Jean-Baptiste Leschenault in Java." url="https://doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.70.9758" volume="70" year="2016 b">Aubriot et al. 2016b</bibRefCitation>
